<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[الخُتَع]</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span>: الدليل الماهر.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
